Raw Text:
Stricken language would be deleted from and underlined language would be added to present law.
Act 797 of the Regular Session
1 State of Arkansas As Engrossed: H4/3/25
A Bill
2 95th General Assembly
3 Regular Session, 2025 HOUSE BILL 1929
4
5 By: Representative McAlindon
6 By: Senator J. Dotson
7
For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT TO CREATE THE RECOGNIZING JUDEA AND SAMARIA
10 ACT; TO PROHIBIT STATE AGENCIES FROM USING THE TERM
11 "WEST BANK" IN OFFICIAL GOVERNMENT MATERIALS; AND FOR
12 OTHER PURPOSES.
